name: Schrodinger's Coin
description: You know how Schrodinger put a cat in a box where it was both alive and dead until someone looked? That's literally your bag of shitcoins right now. Every token in your wallet exists in a quantum state: worth millions and worthless until you check your balance. The moment you look at your wallet? Reality collapses. You're either booking that Dubai trip or applying to your local Mcdonald's. $MAYBE is the first memecoin that doesn't just embrace this truth- it's built on it. Literally all of crypto is Schrodinger's Coin lol. $MAYBE rekt, $MAYBE rich
